brief_title: Stress Reduction and Atherosclerotic CVD in Blacks
brief_summary: To evaluate the effectiveness of stress reduction with Transcendental Meditation (TM) on left ventricular hypertrophy, left ventricular function, blood pressure, psychosocial stress and quality of life, and cardiovascular disease risk factors.
